          "id": "instruction-step-art-007-001",
          "order": 1,
          "instruction": "Whisk the all-purpose flour, baking powder, and fine sea salt; separately whisk the whole-milk ricotta, eggs, whole milk, and fresh lemon zest, then fold the mixtures together until just combined."
